(E. Data Flow Summary) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 564.70 Tm
(Authentication/session flow:) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 548.20 Tm
(- The browser submits credentials to `POST /api/signup` or `POST /api/login`.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 534.70 Tm
(- The server validates inputs, hashes or verifies the password, creates a random session token, and) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 521.20 Tm
(returns it.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 507.70 Tm
(- The browser stores the token in localStorage and sends it in the `Authorization: Bearer` header.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 494.20 Tm
(- The server resolves the token through local JSON or Supabase sessions.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 480.70 Tm
(Profile update flow:) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 464.20 Tm
(- The profile editor collects display name, handle, bio, location, social links, theme, cursor,) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 450.70 Tm
(sparkle, media, and toggle settings.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 437.20 Tm
(- The browser sends the profile payload to `PUT /api/profiles/:handle`.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 423.70 Tm
(- The server verifies the session and profile ownership before saving.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 410.20 Tm
(- Public profile links are saved back onto the user record when possible.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 396.70 Tm
(Media upload flow:) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 380.20 Tm
(- The frontend previews selected files as data URLs.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 366.70 Tm
(- In Supabase mode, the server uploads media to `profile-media` and stores object paths.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 353.20 Tm
(- In local JSON mode, media remains embedded in profile JSON.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 339.70 Tm
(- Public profile media is served through `/api/profiles/:handle/avatar`, `/background`, and) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 326.20 Tm
(`/music`.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 312.70 Tm
(Friends/notifications flow:) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 296.20 Tm
(- Friend requests are stored on the target profile and sent request state is stored on the sender) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 282.70 Tm
(profile.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 269.20 Tm
(- Notifications are rendered from friend requests, tribe invites, and tribe join requests.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 255.70 Tm
(- The frontend refreshes friend and notification state periodically.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 242.20 Tm
